source.name: Economic Indicator Database Search
source.description: The Economic Indicator Database Search provides easy to access time series data for the 12 Economic Indicators produced by the Census Bureau. Data users (business analysts, the press, economic researchers) can use the database for quicker access to the data they need for modeling, trend analyses, and other research.
